wikipedia_page.main: Thomas Davis Fenby (1875 - 4 August 1956) was a British Liberal politician and blacksmith.

response: *Thomas Fenby, a Liberal politician and blacksmith, was born in the town in 1875. He acted as Mayor of Bridlington and represented the town as MP. He died at his Bridlington home in 1956.
